text: The Round-Up (, "Poor young men", i. e. outlaws) is a 1966 Hungarian drama movie directed by Miklós Jancsó and starring János Görbe, Zoltán Latinovits, Tibor Molnár, Gábor Agárdy, András Kozák, Béla Barsi. ==Other websites== * Category:1966 drama movies Category:Hungarian movies Category:Movies directed by Miklós Jancsó
title: The Round-Up (1966 movie)
